<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currency formatting isn't correct when using nl_BE as locale.</p>

<p>Zend_Registry::set('Zend_Currency', new Zend_Currency('nl_BE'));
$this-&gt;currency(50);
Gives as result:
50,00 €</p>

<p>This should be:
€ 50,00</p>

<p>However when using nl_NL as locale the formatting is correct.</p>

<p>Fix:
/Locale/Data/nl_BE.xml</p>

<p>Change currencyFormat &gt; pattern to:
¤#,##0.00</p>

