        <div class="body">
            <p>According to CLDR the format to use for currencies is &gt;#,##0.00 ¤&lt;</p>

<p>This means that ZF produces the correct output.
When you wish to use another output simply give the wished format.
When you feel that there is an error within CLDR please report an issue at <a href="http://cldr.unicode.org">http://cldr.unicode.org</a></p>

<p>You should note that even the actual release of CLDR which is 3 weeks old, provides the same format pattern.</p>

